ondungeon.1:
(Cixot) We’re stuck here alone. This sucks, when can we leave?
(You) But we just got here...
ondungeon.2:
(Tenretni) This place reminds me of a video game I used to play...
(You) We’re playing it right now.
(Cixot) I liked it better back then.
ondungeon.5:
(You) This is a cool dungeon.
(Tenretni) This dungeon is like every other dungeon we’ve been to.
ondungeon.7:
(Tenretmi) So where are we going?
(Cixot) Hopefully somewhere better than this.
ondungeon.10:
(You) Exploring isn’t so bad.
(Cixot) It’s not like we have any other option...
ondungeon.20:
(Tenretni) 20th dungeon. Imagine what’s still in store.
(Cixot) Nothing, this is the end of the programmed dialog.
ondungeon.25: (You) Cixot, sometimes you just make up things to be mad about.

edistou: Relaxing in the sun has left me weak
